Revision history for App-size-dir-diff

    0.4.1 2020-09-19

     - Add description of /tmp/first_hash file-to-memory copy behavior
     - Add option -n, Print files that do not exist in the first path
     - Add brackets + number indicating for which path the file count is

    0.4.0 2020-09-19

     - Add option -e, Prompt user if duplicate files should be deleted
       NOTE: ENTER-key can be held down to delete many files at once

    0.3.9 2020-08-31

     - Move revision history into Changes
     - Update PREREQ_PM entries to match script dependencies

    0.3.8 2020-08-31

     - Remove Build.PL
     - Use directory structure lib/App/size/dir/diff.pm 

    0.3.7 2020-08-31

     - Rename script and use conventional package/module name
     - Quote version string

    0.3.6 2020-08-30

     - Fix indentation
     - Remove README.pod
     - Improve CPAN module files

    0.3.5 2020-08-30
 
     - Prompt user for (Y/N) on delete (and do not assume Y)
     - Improve help and CPAN module files

    0.3.4 2020-08-30

     - Initial release

    $ size_dir_diff -d /usr/src/BPi/device-tree /usr/src/BPi/device-tree.copy
    Files in /usr/src/BPi/device-tree.copy that differ from files in /usr/src/BPi/device-tree:
    Files in /usr/src/BPi/device-tree.copy that have a duplicate in /usr/src/BPi/device-tree:
    /sun7i-a20-bananapi.dtb
